title: Edexcel past papers for all maths subjects since Jun 2006
description:
All Edexcel past papers for AS/A2 modules (Core, Mechanics, Further Pure, Stats, and Decision) for Jun 2006 to Jan 2008. Also papers for 'Pure maths A level' and 'Maths B' which I am not familiar with but included anyway, in case anyone is doing this course. Also all the mark schemes.

Good luck to anyone doing A levels/AS this year!
